Sony has sold 3 million PlayStation VR headsets, the company announced. The company stated that 21.9 million PSVR “games and experiences” have also been sold worldwide. “We want to take this opportunity to thank the developers and publishers who have brought some of the most engaging titles to the platform,” said Sony. “In addition to the robust catalogue of nearly 340 PSVR games and experiences worldwide, there’s still plenty to look forward to.” The company further disclosed the top 10 games played on the PSVR platform to date.